!!!
html
  head
    title Zeke Sikelianos, Internet Designer/Developer
    meta(name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1")

    link(href='//fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Roboto+Slab:400,700|Open+Sans', rel='stylesheet', type='text/css')
    link(href='/assets/styles.css', rel='stylesheet', type='text/css')

    script(src="/assets/app.js")

  body
    section.first
      article

        img(src="/assets/images/anthropomorphs2.png")

        aside
          h1 Zeke<br /> Sikelianos

          :markdown
            I'm a designer and software developer in the [San Francisco](http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Emperor_Norton) Bay Area. I work at [Heroku](http://heroku.com), where I design and build open-source tools to help creative people build magical things on the Internet. I believe [information wants to be free](http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hacker_ethic), and that you can create beautiful things with computers.

          :markdown
            Find me on [Twitter](http://twitter.com/zeke),
            [GitHub](http://github.com/zeke), and [Cargo](http://cargocollective.com/zeke).

    section
      article

        h2
          a(id="projects" href="#projects") Projects

    section
      article

        ul
          - each project in public.resume._data.projects
            li(id=project.slug)
              h3
                a(href=project.website)= project.name
                a.permalink(href="#"+project.slug) #
              p= project.description

        h2
          a(id="jobs" href="#jobs") Places I've Worked

        ul
          - each job in public.resume._data.jobs
            li(id=job.slug)
              h3
                a(href=job.website)= job.organization
                em= job.location
                a.permalink(href="#"+job.slug) #

              p= job.description
              p.paltry
                = job.start
                = " - "
                = job.end

        h2
          a(id="schools" href="#schools") Schools I've Attended

        ul
          - each school in public.resume._data.schools
            li(id=school.slug)
              h3
                a(href=school.website)= school.organization
                em=  school.location
                a.permalink(href="#"+school.slug) #
              p= school.description
              p.paltry
                = school.start
                = " - "
                = school.end

        h2
          a(id="fin" href="#fin") The End

        :markdown
          In case you missed it at the top, I'm [zeke](http://twitter.com/zeke) on Twitter and
          [zeke](http://github.com/zeke) on Github. Please send me something cool. And thanks for scrolling. For that, you deserve a [prize](http://asciiface.zeke.xxx/).

      footer
